  "description": [
    "Louisiana Official Tells Kennedy Integration Will Fail Forced Mixing Of Roces Defeats Itself In The End The Record Shows Enforced integration leads inevitably to either an allwhite or an allNegro community This fact was declared by Wade O Martin Secretary of State of the State of Louisiana in an open letter to Presi dent Kennedy recently When you succeed in forcing com plete integration in Mississippi and other areas where the Negro population out numbers the white those areas will be abandoned by most white people just as Washington D C was virtually aban doned declared the Secretary of State Use of Force The use of force and the courts as is now being done to bring about the in tegration of the white and Negro races is leading to national suicide and the only way to prevent the nation from committing suicide is to revert back to the democratic processes that were pro vided in our constitution according to Martin Here are some of the things that Martin said on this subject We want to help Negroes as well as whites nevertheless human nature can not be changed overnight Most of the white people of Mississippi Louisiana New York"
  ],
